ğŸ” Recommended & Reliable Automation Approach

âœ… Use a PostSync Job in YAML (with oc/kubectl) to restart the VM

This is the best practice in your case because:

Benefit	Why it matters

âœ… One commit	Resize + restart happen together
âœ… Fully automated	No manual step or second commit needed
âœ… GitOps-friendly	Everything is defined in YAML and version-controlled
